      "content": "interesting. so it's basically this tiny, invisible ecosystem constantly fighting and shifting. it seems almost chaotic how they're all working on their own at the same time just to keep the starter alive. do you think the process is mostly predictable, or is there a level of randomness to how these microbes behave in the jar?",
